.BR putwchar ()
T}	Thread safety	MT-Safe
.TE
.SH STANDARDS
C11, POSIX.1-2008.
.SH HISTORY
POSIX.1-2001, C99.
.SH NOTES
The behavior of
.BR putwchar ()
depends on the
.B LC_CTYPE
category of the
current locale.
.P
It is reasonable to expect that
.BR putwchar ()
will actually write
the multibyte sequence corresponding to the wide character
.IR wc .
